review_blob:
No flavor, no aroma, just slightly better than water..
Good for when you just want one can in your hand and join people in social gathering..

This was the first ever beer I tasted. It was enough to discourage me trying beer again.. But in India, some places you dont have much options so I had to settle for kingfisher strong more often.. Its not something you will search through the store or something you get craving for, but once you are accustomed with its taste its really nice.. Its best thing with spicy Indian food, only if you have developed the taste for both..
This is my favourite beer for regular weekends. Its far better than blue moon any day..
